name: Neimoidian Pilot
Lore: 'Trade Federation Neimodian pilots are some of the most desired in the galaxy due to their willingness to follow orders.',
Text: 'Deploys -2 at Naboo. When deployed aboard your battleship, you may activate 1 Force. Adds 2 to the power of any starship he pilots. Forfeit +2 while piloting.',
